-- Djokovic Starts Wimbledon Title Defense Against Ferrero
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2012-06-22T09:37:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/djokovic-starts-wimbledon-title-defense-against-ferrero.html
Novak Djokovic of Serbia will start
the defense of his Wimbledon title against former French Open
champion Juan Carlos Ferrero of Spain.  The top seeded Djokovic was drawn in the same half as six-
time champion  Roger Federer , meaning the two may meet in the
semifinals. The third-seeded Swiss plays Spain’s Albert Ramos in
the first round.  French Open champion Rafael Nadal of Spain plays Thomaz
Bellucci of Brazil. The second-seeded Spaniard was drawn in the
same half as  Andy Murray . The fourth-seeded Briton plays
Russia’s Nikolay Davydenko.  The Wimbledon championships starts June 25 at the All
England Club in southwest London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Danielle Rossingh at 
 drossingh@bloomberg.net  